<l:eg_i_low>
Low Water areas often occur near the coast. Submarines (4) must maneuver more carefully than in <l:eg_deep_water>. Battleships (3) and Transport Ships (2) have no disadvantage compared to Deep Water.

Battleships can bombard the coast from the Low Water areas. 
